Go to Anaconda's official website "https://www.anaconda.com/" and copy the link of "download for linux"<br />
And input `bash Anaconda3-5.0.1-Linux-x86_64.sh` in the terminal.<br />
After thatï¼Œwe 'll change the configure for anaconda.<br />
Add the install path to .bashrc `export PATH=$PATH:your anaconda path` and run`source ~/.bashrc` to make the change activate.<br />
Then we can run`conda --version` to check.
